Whether you need to transport a few chairs, a long panel or a large computer desk, our line of Raymond trucks and dollies is sure to include just item you're looking for. With a variety of heavy duty caster and wheel options and steering designed for one person, Raymond's moving equipment is perfect for schools, businesses and churches – anywhere large equipment is used.To shop our selection of Raymond trucks, dollies and racks, just click a link above. You can order online or call our sales team to order by phone. Just give us a call at 1-800-260-2776.











